            "processed": "<p>Slicer, or 3D Slicer, is a free, open source software package for visualization and image analysis. 3D Slicer is natively designed to be available on multiple platforms, including Windows, Linux and Mac Os X.</p><p>Source code: <a href=\"https://github.com/Slicer/Slicer\">https://github.com/Slicer/Slicer</a></p>",
